text: Vladimír Kejř (20 January 1929 - 9 May 1981) is a Czech gymnast. He competed at the 1952 Summer Olympics and the 1956 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1929 births Category:1981 deaths Category:People from Úvaly Category:Czech male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Czechoslovakia Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1956 Summer Olympics
